content: I think I can apply these tips by being more mindful of my snacking habits and planning my snacks in advance. I've been doing well with meal prep, but I need to work on planning my snacks too. I also want to try to find healthier alternatives to my favorite junk foods, like baked sweet potato fries instead of regular potato chips. And, I need to remember to be kind to myself when I do give in to cravings, because it's not the end of the world. By the way, I've been making sweet potato fries at home a lot lately, and I've even tried different seasonings like paprika and garlic powder.
